{"tid":808770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱向網上結識騙徒匯款逾億　消息指女事主視為小數目","createTime":"2018-09-06T14:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T15:10:42.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f686664c4307c141f24a1d45d43e10719d5ddc5","tid":808770,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"一名女子在網上交友平台結識一名自稱身處海外的男工程師，報稱4年間向對方匯款合共1億8千萬元，是有紀錄以來最大宗的網上情緣騙案，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，66歲的事主與騙徒發展成網絡戀人，但一直無見過面，事主曾向騙徒轉帳超過200次，由於身家豐厚，視為小數目。"},{"pid":"a8cdda3e11d5524dd8ab3f828358d0a5cb328490","tid":808770,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"揀我啦姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸窮撚00後"},{"pid":"3b97af63abfb58b147ccf236825934864cb3c615","tid":808770,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗黑錢唔係將d錢由唔見得光變做見得光咩？依家調轉都係洗黑錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你點知本身嗰筆唔係黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n四年分200次過數銀行冇舟到<br />\n然後話情騙走佬差佬想查都去唔到咁遠查<br />\n<br />\n筆錢隨時已經轉左地球一圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>筆錢原本已經係銀行，就算本身係黑錢都已經洗左。依家匯完錢，銀行冇舟到冇人查，但要自己去報警等人查下咁得意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果事主唔係最終收款目標又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢呢D咁低調又有錢先最易洗</blockquote>我唔明你想講咩？<br />\n1.佢d錢本身已經係銀行，依樣已經係洗黑錢最難既步驟。<br />\n2. 假設佢真係洗黑錢，佢d錢已經順利匯左俾人，冇人懷疑（至少表面上），已經過左骨，點解佢要報警引人注意？唔係報左警人地就信你架，如果係全世界都用依招喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上咪有人話銀行可能已經查緊只係未有證據<br />\n(4年，200條transaction去一個戶口，總數1.8億，如果AML有認真做Periodic Review會撈到唔奇)<br />\n<br />\n宜家先發制人話自己俾個未見過嘅鬼佬呃，佢咁講真係吹佢唔漲，你要查咪捉個鬼佬返來查</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">銀莊都係為錢，電腦KYC有心做點會捉唔撚到丫？成200單今日先出聲？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成單野咪又係大龍鳳，洗手銀莊警犬MA四家鬥扮傻咁囉！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7c1d3d5500897e7db0334a390acb0b0488b5fb1b","tid":808770,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8cdda3e11d5524dd8ab3f828358d0a5cb328490","tid":808770,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"揀我啦姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸窮撚00後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"爆一個post留過名嘅人平均分,都每人10幾廿萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd024d87cc74ab186d23a0b95005b94cf711e38","tid":808770,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"小數目就咪撚報警啦<br />\n成件事咁古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0273802e4c7ffc3a67227a7ff6c0a6b6a762917","tid":808770,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd024d87cc74ab186d23a0b95005b94cf711e38","tid":808770,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"小數目就咪撚報警啦<br />\n成件事咁古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"佢見對方失蹤，係驚佢有事咋。"},{"pid":"3425758366cd944ecf44f4c71ad0fb9ea9887b61","tid":808770,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小數目就咪撚報警啦<br />\n成件事咁古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>佢見對方失蹤，係驚佢有事咋。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你係警犬打狗，文盲定白癡？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"}]}